<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Donor Listing</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .clouds {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 12%, transparent 13%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 75% 35%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 15%, transparent 16%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 45% 75%, rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 10%, transparent 11%);
            animation: float 15s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateX(-15px); }
        }
        
        .content {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            padding: 50px 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            max-width: 600px;
            z-index: 2;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .icon {
            font-size: 4em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            font-size: 2.8em;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ffffff, #f0fdf4);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            margin: 0 0 30px 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .steps {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .step {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: left;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        
        .step-number {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 20px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .step-text {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="clouds"></div>
    <div class="content">
        <span class="icon">üè™</span>
        <h1>Donors List Surplus Food</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Businesses and individuals can easily create listings for their surplus food</p>
        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <div class="step-text">Provide food details and quantity</div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <div class="step-text">Set expiry date and pickup location</div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <div class="step-text">Publish listing for recipients to see</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
